{
  "id": "adv_main_01_09_10",
  "title": "星見編2章36話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pretty-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_10-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "ふう……緊張しちゃいました",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Phew… I was so nervous.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_10-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "でも、衣装のイメージをしっかり伝えられたし\n有意義な打ち合わせになったと思うよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But you were able to communicate exactly what you wanted the costumes to be like‚\nso I think the meeting was very productive.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 8.079436036160118,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 10.972857046127354
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_10-chs002.m4a",
      "text": "そう……ですか。ううん、私もそう思います\nすみれちゃんのおかげですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Do you… really think so? No‚ yeah. I think so‚ too.\nAnd I have Sumire to thank.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 16.906190379460657,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 19.53952371279396
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_10-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "確かに、奥山さんの登場は計算外だったけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s for sure. Though Sumire showing up was not part of the plan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.53952371279399,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 24.120181194941207
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_10-chs003.m4a",
      "text": "え？　計算外……って、どういうことですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Plan? What do you mean… “plan”?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.120181194941207,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 29.686847861607873
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_10-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん……\nもうバラしちゃうんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "{user}…\nBlowing our cover already?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.02018119494121,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 0,
          "startTime": 29.686847861607873
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 33.26561349924061
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_10-chs004.m4a",
      "text": "え？　……お、お姉ちゃん！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? S-Saki?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.26561349924061,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 36.28146380479786
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pop-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 36.28146380479789
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_10-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ご、ごめん……つい口が滑って……\nでも、もうそろそろいいだろう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-sorry. A slip of the tongue.\nBut I think it’s about time we tell her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.7147971381312,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_10-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "そうですね。打ち合わせは無事に終わった\nみたいですし、話しちゃいましょうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You’re right. Now that the meeting is done without a hitch‚\nlet’s go ahead and tell her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 45.748130471464535,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 49.136856162836025
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_10-chs005.m4a",
      "text": "え？　え？　……ええ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Huh? Huh？？？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 49.136856162836025,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 52.270189496169365
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_10-ski003.m4a",
      "text": "ごめんね、千紗\n今回の衣装打ち合わせの人選なんだけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sorry‚ Chisa.\nSo‚ when we chose our representatives for the costume meeting…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.503522829502685,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_10-ski004.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんにも協力してもらって\n私達が選ばれるように仕組んでいたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I got a little help from {user}\nand made it so we would get chosen.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.43685616283602,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 63.314116483162884
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_10-chs006.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうだったの？\nでも、いつから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Y-you did?\nBut when did you arrange that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.61411648316287,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 67.58078314982954
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_10-ski005.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんが\n打ち合わせの話をする直前、私から相談したのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Maybe she led me here‚ {user}‚\nspoke to us about the costume meeting‚ I spoke with him in private.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.78078314982956,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 73.64744981649625
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_10-ski006.m4a",
      "text": "どうしたら千紗は\n自分に自信を持ってくれるかなって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I asked him how my little sister\ncould gain some self-confidence.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.08078314982956,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 77.98078314982956
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_10-ski007.m4a",
      "text": "千紗が洋服選びとかコーディネートのセンスに\n長けているのは、事実だったし……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And you are very good at picking out outfits.\nThat wasn’t a lie.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 80.61411648316289,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_10-ski008.m4a",
      "text": "これをきっかけに、自信をつけてもらえないかな……\nって思ったの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So we thought that perhaps we could use that as an opportunity\nto give you confidence.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.84744981649622,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 88.20237954977259
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_10-chs007.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ……全然連絡取れなかったのも\n出ないようにしてた、ってこと？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ the reason I wasn’t able to contact you\nwas because you ignored me on purpose?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.50237954977256,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 94.92517936053973
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_10-ski009.m4a",
      "text": "うん、私に頼らずに乗り切ってほしかったから\nでも、こっそり様子は覗いてたのよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah. I wanted you to get through this on your own‚ not relying on me.\nBut I did sneak peeks at how you were doing.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.4918460272064,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_10-ski010.m4a",
      "text": "オロオロしてるのを見て\nこっちまでハラハラしてたんだから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "When I saw how nervous you were\nit made my hands start to shake‚ too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 104.70851269387317,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 107.10851269387318
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_10-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "そ……そういうこと、だったんだね……\n二人で、私のこと騙して……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh… so that’s what happened.\nYou both lied to me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.00851269387321,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 116.04694512278695
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_10-ski011.m4a",
      "text": "ち、違うのよ、千紗\n騙そうって気持ちはなくって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "N-no‚ Chisa!\nWe didn’t mean any harm.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 118.48027845612025,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_hope-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 120.94694512278691
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 120.94694512278691
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_10-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "お、お姉ちゃんの……バカバカバカ……っ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-Saki‚ you’re… stupid‚ stupid‚ stupid!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.94694512278691,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "2d-01",
      "startTime": 124.92424672038213
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_10/sud_vo_adv_main_01_09_10-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "本当に、心配したし……不安だったんだよ\nもしかして、事故に遭ったんじゃないかって……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I really was worried about you… I was scared.\nI was scared you’d gotten in an accident.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.39091338704873,
